Entries.default: "Captain... is it not too late to simply sail away?"
"The Rauataians don't do anything in half measures, do they?"
"I don't have a head for politics and schemes, but it's hard not to think of Duc Aevar, and what happened after."
"Don't suppose it ain't too late to drop anchor and let these sad bastards off one another? We could swoop in after, pick up the pieces."
"Sometimes the ends justify the means... Sometimes you've got to do things you don't want to do..."
